		<h1>Terry Tempest Williams Accepts Stegner Award, Struggles for Coherence</h1>
		<h2><i></i></h2>
		<div class="text-feature_print">
							<p>By Jenny Shank, 11-03-05</p>
			
							<table width="25" align="right" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
					<tr>
						<td>&nbsp;</td>
						<td><img src="http://www.newwest.net/images/thumbnails_feature/tempest.jpg" class="thumbnail-feature" border="0" align="right" width="200" height="266" /></td>
